Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:31.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:40.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谛め”がくれた 安楽沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:46.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつからだっただろう？ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらずにいてと愿うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:53.53,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わりゆく时に生きる仆ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:56.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の声を…言い得ぬ梦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.72,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と繋がった空へ　响かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:04.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと强く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:08.31,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:11.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“今度こそは…”つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤さえも无駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:21.43,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:24.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪む世界　走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覚のその向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:33.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真実”と　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:31.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:40.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放棄」所帶給我的 安樂但停滯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:46.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從什麼時候開始  突然間開始變得閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望永恆不變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:53.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷改變地世界生存的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:56.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心聲…無法說出夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.72,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹著 這與你相連的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:04.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更用力地…用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:08.31,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我揮去所有的淚水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:11.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將永不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這些傷痕也不會讓它白費
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快地 前往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:21.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這雙翅膀被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:24.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奔出 這扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著我所感受到的彼方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:33.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的「真實」去加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
