Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃之軍團？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(440,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃之王…為何在此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王…那麼說他就是統帥黃之軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(593,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等級9的超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(470,430)}<Buster Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你設計好的啊 黃之聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(567,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 難道是還要和你說日安麼 紅之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你假惺惺啥啊 明擺著是在埋伏我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實的1秒是這裏的17分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是故意的 根本不可能在這裏見面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說的那麼過分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要讓違反互不侵犯條約
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊了我可愛的部下並迫使其損失全部的點數的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤之軍團的某一位負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(342,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而來到此地的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是他偷藏了「災禍之鎧」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後交給櫻紅之車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(480,430)}<Cherry Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了引出仁子 腥紅之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(512,430)}<Scarlet Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在互不侵犯條約寫著有這麼一條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍團的成員因為違反條約遭受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(230,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並被迫強制卸載「Brain Burst」的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個軍團可以從襲擊方的軍團中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(565,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選出任何一個人並讓其遭受同樣的困境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那個任何一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就是紅之軍團的當主腥紅之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(411,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(577,430)}<Scarlet Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切明擺的就只是為了能使自己達到等級10的必須的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個首級其中之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:27.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(662,393)}Obligation ; 宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}這樣啊 是這個目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}您能理解那是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是條約上也寫了這麼一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說可以選隨機的一名進行復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但軍團當主自己裁決違反者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其點數全數剝奪的情況下就可以不作追究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 但我也聽到了一些傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎就已經嘗試過了 不過卻完敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要再挑戰的話 那是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個傢伙到底下次什麼時候出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候可以打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能現在馬上就解決他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來就只能用你來當沙包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個陷阱 仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先暫時下線吧 然後等下次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這無限制中立舞台中是沒辦法隨時下線的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要從這裏離開的話 只能到各地設置的退出點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統就是這樣設定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我們就先去退出點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裏最近的退出點是池袋和陽光都市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣 看來都要打上個一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吶 聲波那個混帳也有誤算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(358,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 雖說那個混賬為了我一個人聚集起了那麼一幫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們這裏還有另外一個王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事 黑之睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(510,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於接下來將要發生的嘉年華盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您能在旁靜靜的觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 黃之聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問什麼我要聽從你的話按你的意圖行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是個不懂事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還給你準備了這樣的一份大禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代的王 紅之騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(484,430)}<Red Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代的王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們戰鬥至今就是為了這麼個無聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎惡 互相掠奪 互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們統領各自的軍團戰鬥至今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(467,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是因為我們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是因為我們是競爭對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你的戰鬥方式啊 睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(567,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有機會在現實生活中見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你肯定能成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是想和你成為死黨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想和以命相搏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是這麼想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 騎士 剛才那些話我們可不能聽了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(243,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦 才不是那種意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就像你說的一樣 騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(556,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也挺喜歡你的 當然只是尊敬的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你能懂我 睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(526,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣 這只是握手的代替形式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告·擁抱致死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Death By Embracing>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 學姐 學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Zero Field>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮Louts 你竟然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你還是不能擺脫那次的背叛的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真沒想到你靠那點覺悟目標等級10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑得我肚子疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 強化外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 紅之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一旦強化武裝 就會失去機動力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在應該先撤退到陽光城市的退出點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我來擋一會兒 你快帶著主人走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那樣的話 你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在打倒紅之王后 一定會盯上主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓他們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無限制空間裏 痛覺是普通對戰的兩倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就到坑洞的邊緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到那裏 就能抱著學姐和仁子一口氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無用的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚人的旋轉木馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Siuy Go-Round>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間在旋轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是看上去在旋轉罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的 不會這麼容易就能還清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你根本沒有欠我什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾次你才能明白啊 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你只會用腦的那句話我收回 藍色之樁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(609,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過30秒 聲波的必殺技就會失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來聽說你有點本事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只是靠給人當肉盾混飯的啊 藍色之樁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(620,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你死之前給我記清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉你的人就是本大爺撒克遜人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(565,430)}<Saxon>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你這種笨蛋的名字…不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆戰槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lightning Cyan Spike>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就交給你了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雨釘刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 你果然是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我引以為傲的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪姬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(472,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在從這女人靈魂中輸出到虛擬角色上的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被零填滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有鬥志的超頻連接者是無法操縱虛擬對戰角色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有力量直面自己內心的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會連站立都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Burst就是這樣一個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的傷痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶著睡蓮跑吧 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(380,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(525,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然藍色之樁奮不顧身為我們爭取到了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(272,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我還沒有膽小到能在這個時候說跑就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要丟下同伴自己逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個徹頭徹尾的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就隨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃之聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的必殺技槽應該已經全空了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回該我們反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是被我打敗了的話就會從這個世界消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 強化外裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要應付在我背後的近戰型對手就行了 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被他們打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就帶著睡蓮飛走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(452,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們擔心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是個固定炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊貼著它打的話 它也就像鐵塊一樣毫無還手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的對手可是紅之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你們印象深刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充數的就不要在這裏礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁力波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Maganetron Wave>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金屬很容易被磁鐵吸上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我的必殺技只能持續13秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽透你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到要和金屬系中最難應付的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊型對手進行近身戰的情況時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好要躲過對方的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用對方的力道反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你的反應速度 這個作戰策略是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你平時一副無能的樣子 幹得還不賴嘛 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(667,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干擾波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找出來 烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是他手下某個黃色傢伙的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電擊理療
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Electric Therapy>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們把紅之王給扒光了之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那睡會兒吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是多麼狼狽多麼難看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有半點王的威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底也就是紅色的暴發戶和黑色的叛徒罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 紅之王也只不過是這等貨色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 把她的鐵皮全剝了 從裏面拖出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能容忍這種情形嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種完結的方式是你願意看到的嗎 黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說加速是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Burst是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所謂達到前無古人的Lv10的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道比對一個男人的回憶更加廉價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在那種地方睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要斬破了所有的障礙 橫掃千軍萬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算流盡最後一滴血也要實現你的野心不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和騎士怎麼被你說得像是戀人關係似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(257,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎 你是我的第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 別老趴在地上 試試單手插入地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是地面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的自己能解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去照看一下那丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 擒拿系的技能對我來說大都無效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然和你們無冤無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和我戰鬥的人必將嘗到某個部位殘缺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在這個比平時多兩倍的區域裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要現在才叫喊著「不要啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 我現在還在充電啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到現在才出來攪局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來妨礙我的嗎 黑之睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(539,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了你背叛我們 把朋友的頭砍下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在哪裏做著什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會不會想起自己再也回不到加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和讓他變成這樣的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話 是絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平常的對戰也就罷了 沒想到居然是偷襲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一點誤會了 黃之聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(526,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的首級和紅之騎士的份量對我來說一樣重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Red Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 再告訴你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 從第一次見到你開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就超級討厭你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腥雨 剩下的外裝再充電完畢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(255,430)}<Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉 掩護她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(379,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再休息一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉 干擾電波的來源在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(281,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和那時候…不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快 這就是Lv9之間的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著吧 加速世界開始以來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是首次Lv9之間的正面惡鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的必殺技槽差不多滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才開始亮真傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮的必殺技大概會是直接攻擊系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(230,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反聲波應該是幻覺系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(353,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聲波的必殺技打出來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(312,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮的致命一擊到底能不能命中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(258,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是決勝點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告·貫通致死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Death By Piercing>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意義的命運之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Feudal Fortune Wheel>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:40.86,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,396)}Absolution ; 寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}下回 Absolution 寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在決戰的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}理當被寬恕的 能是由愛而生的罪麼
